snippet.title: Rain Rain Go Away Song with Diana's Family
snippet.description:
Rain Rain Go Away Song with Diana's Family! Funny song facing the rain with a request to leave. Dad, mom, brother, sister and baby want to play, but the rain does not want to go away.
The song excellently raises the mood. It is very rhythmic, you can even dance with the child.
Instagram Diana: https://www.instagram.com/kidsdianashow/
